data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Lehigh Acres! This stunning, newer-built 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom masterpiece is a true gem. As you step inside, you're greeted by a magnificent 72 x 96 custom-made Bronze double entry door, setting the tone for the elegant details this home has.   Luxury abounds with 2x2 porcelain floors that grace every inch of this home, paired with touch dimmers controlling exquisite 4” flush mount lights throughout. The kitchen, dining, and living areas boast impressive 12ft ceilings, creating an open and airy atmosphere. The granite kitchen island is a focal point, perfect for culinary adventures and gatherings.  Organizational convenience is key with innovative ceiling-hung shelving storage measuring 8x4x5, ensuring every item has its place. Smart home enthusiasts will appreciate the Nest Wireless Thermostat and the Ring Door Bell Pro with spotlight cam for added security.  But that's not all - this home is built to withstand the elements with impact doors and windows. It's truly one of a kind, and with its incredible features, it won't be available for long. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional residence!
